        <updateDate>2022-03-17T20:57:57Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Preserving the MotorCities Heritage Act</strong></p> <p>This bill extends through FY2036 the authority of the Department of the Interior to make grants or furnish technical assistance for the MotorCities National Heritage Area in Michigan. </p> <p>The bill also increases the maximum amount of funding that may be appropriated&nbsp;for the heritage area. </p> <p>Finally, the bill waives, for FY2022-FY2023, the matching funds requirement for the heritage area.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
